rows.label: tlk46500174_02_msg0001
rows.name: Oh, the tragedy of it all...

rows.label: tlk46500174_02_msg0002
rows.name:
To think the day would come when I
would have to enter the date of Lady
Fan's death into the annals of Acedia...

rows.label: tlk46500174_02_msg0003
rows.name:
The children loved her so.
I don't think they really understand
yet that she is gone forever...

rows.label: tlk46500174_02_msg0004
rows.name:
And we will never again hear her
beautiful voice ring out in song...
